lead_paragraph: Any thoughts of top-ranked Notre Dame looking past Valparaiso and peeking ahead to Wednesday's clash with No. 2 Connecticut were quickly put to rest Sunday as the Fighting Irish used a 26-0 start to coast to a 114-54 win over Valparaiso.

headline.print_headline: Young Scores 20 as No. 1 Notre Dame Routs Valparaiso 114-54
